<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="title">创建配送订单</view>
    <view class="subtitle">填写最小下单信息，先跑通“创建订单 -> 启动配送 -> 查看状态”。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="service-banner status-{{serviceState}}">
    {{serviceMessage}}
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-caption">收货人信息只在创建订单时填写，不再作为首页默认身份保存。</view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">配送员 ID</text>
      <input class="input" value="{{senderId}}" data-key="senderId" bindinput="handleInput" />
      <view class="field-help">演示默认配送员 ID 已预填，可直接联调。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">收货人 ID</text>
      <input class="input" value="{{receiverId}}" data-key="receiverId" bindinput="handleInput" />
      <view class="field-help">联调接收端建议保持与通知页中的用户 ID 一致。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">目标 AprilTag ID</text>
      <input class="input" type="number" value="{{targetId}}" data-key="targetId" bindinput="handleInput" />
      <view class="field-help">演示默认目标 ID 已预填，若切换标签请同步修改。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">设备名</text>
      <input class="input" value="{{deviceName}}" data-key="deviceName" bindinput="handleInput" />
      <view class="field-help" wx:if="{{serviceDefaultDevice}}">当前后端默认设备：{{serviceDefaultDevice}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">备注</text>
      <textarea class="textarea" value="{{note}}" data-key="note" bindinput="handleInput"></textarea>
    </view>

    <view class="field-help">点击“创建并启动”后，会立即向设备发送“开始配送”指令。</view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="ghost-btn" loading="{{creating}}" bindtap="createOnly">仅创建</button>
      <button class="primary-btn" loading="{{creating}}" bindtap="createAndStart">创建并启动</button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="page-footnote">
    <view>全国大学生嵌入式芯片与系统设计竞赛</view>
    <view class="page-footnote-team">地线引力队</view>
  </view>
</view>
